                    "Text": "<?php\n\nnamespace App\\Jobs;\n\nuse App\\Models\\PlagiarismCheck;\nuse App\\Services\\Plagiarism\\CertificateGenerator;\nuse App\\Services\\Plagiarism\\PlagiarismService;\nuse Illuminate\\Bus\\Queueable;\nuse Illuminate\\Contracts\\Queue\\ShouldQueue;\nuse Illuminate\\Foundation\\Bus\\Dispatchable;\nuse Illuminate\\Queue\\InteractsWithQueue;\nuse Illuminate\\Queue\\SerializesModels;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Log;\n\nclass ProcessPlagiarismCheck implements ShouldQueue\n{\n    use Dispatchable, InteractsWithQueue, Queueable, SerializesModels;\n\n    public int $tries = 3;\n    public int $timeout = 600; // 10 minutes\n    public int $backoff = 60; // Retry after 60 seconds\n\n    public function __construct(\n        public PlagiarismCheck $check\n    ) {}\n\n    public function handle(PlagiarismService $service): void\n    {\n        Log::info(\"Processing plagiarism check #{$this->check->id}\");\n\n        // Update status to processing\n        $this->check->update([\n            'status' => PlagiarismCheck::STATUS_PROCESSING,\n            'started_at' => now(),\n            'error_message' => null,\n        ]);\n\n        try {\n            // Perform the check\n            $result = $service->check($this->check);\n\n            // Update with results\n            $this->check->update([\n                'status' => PlagiarismCheck::STATUS_COMPLETED,\n                'similarity_score' => $result['score'],\n                'similarity_sources' => $result['sources'],\n                'detailed_report' => $result['report'],\n                'provider' => $service->getProvider(),\n                'completed_at' => now(),\n            ]);\n\n            Log::info(\"Plagiarism check #{$this->check->id} completed. Score: {$result['score']}%\");\n\n            // Generate certificate\n            $generator = new CertificateGenerator($this->check);\n            $generator->generate();\n\n            Log::info(\"Certificate generated for check #{$this->check->id}\");\n\n        } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n            Log::error(\"Plagiarism check #{$this->check->id} failed: \" . $e->getMessage());\n\n            $this->check->update([\n                'status' => PlagiarismCheck::STATUS_FAILED,\n                'error_message' => $e->getMessage(),\n                'completed_at' => now(),\n            ]);\n\n            // Re-throw to trigger retry if applicable\n            if ($this->attempts() < $this->tries) {\n                throw $e;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    public function failed(\\Throwable $exception): void\n    {\n        Log::error(\"Plagiarism check job failed permanently for #{$this->check->id}: \" . $exception->getMessage());\n\n        $this->check->update([\n            'status' => PlagiarismCheck::STATUS_FAILED,\n            'error_message' => 'Proses gagal setelah beberapa percobaan: ' . $exception->getMessage(),\n            'completed_at' => now(),\n        ]);\n    }\n}"
                  }
                ],
                "status": "Success"
              }
            ]

                    "Text": "<?php\n\nnamespace App\\Services\\Plagiarism;\n\nuse App\\Models\\DocumentFingerprint;\nuse App\\Models\\Ethesis;\nuse App\\Models\\PlagiarismCheck;\nuse App\\Models\\Setting;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Collection;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Log;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Storage;\nuse Smalot\\PdfParser\\Parser as PdfParser;\n\nclass PlagiarismService\n{\n    protected string $provider;\n    protected array $config;\n\n    public function __construct()\n    {\n        $this->provider = Setting::get('plagiarism_provider', 'internal');\n        $this->loadConfig();\n    }\n\n    protected function loadConfig(): void\n    {\n        $this->config = [\n            'provider' => $this->provider,\n            'similarity_threshold_pass' => (float) Setting::get('plagiarism_pass_threshold', 25),\n            'similarity_threshold_warning' => (float) Setting::get('plagiarism_warning_threshold', 15),\n            'min_words_to_check' => (int) Setting::get('plagiarism_min_words', 100),\n            'chunk_size' => 100, // words per chunk\n        ];\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Process a plagiarism check\n     */\n    public function check(PlagiarismCheck $check): array\n    {\n        Log::info(\"Starting plagiarism check #{$check->id} with provider: {$this->provider}\");\n\n        return match($this->provider) {\n            'internal' => $this->checkInternal($check),\n            'ithenticate' => $this->checkIthenticate($check),\n            'turnitin' => $this->checkTurnitin($check),\n            'copyleaks' => $this->checkCopyleaks($check),\n            default => $this->checkInternal($check),\n        };\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Internal checking against E-Thesis database\n     */\n    protected function checkInternal(PlagiarismCheck $check): array\n    {\n        // 1. Extract text from uploaded document\n        $filePath = Storage::disk('local')->path($check->file_path);\n        $documentText = $this->extractText($filePath, $check->file_type);\n        \n        if (empty($documentText)) {\n            throw new \\Exception('Tidak dapat mengekstrak teks dari dokumen. Pastikan file PDF tidak terenkripsi.');\n        }\n\n        $wordCount = DocumentFingerprint::countWords($documentText);\n        \n        if ($wordCount < $this->config['min_words_to_check']) {\n            throw new \\Exception(\"Dokumen terlalu pendek. Minimal {$this->config['min_words_to_check']} kata.\");\n        }\n\n        // 2. Normalize and chunk the document\n        $normalizedText = DocumentFingerprint::normalizeText($documentText);\n        $chunks = DocumentFingerprint::chunkText($normalizedText, $this->config['chunk_size']);\n        \n        // 3. Store fingerprint\n        $check->fingerprint()->updateOrCreate(\n            ['documentable_id' => $check->id, 'documentable_type' => PlagiarismCheck::class],\n            [\n                'content_text' => $documentText,\n                'content_chunks' => $chunks,\n                'content_hash' => DocumentFingerprint::hashContent($documentText),\n                'word_count' => $wordCount,\n            ]\n        );\n\n        // Update word count in check\n        $check->update(['word_count' => $wordCount]);\n\n        // 4. Compare with existing E-Thesis documents\n        $matchedSources = $this->compareWithDatabase($chunks, $check->member_id);\n\n        // 5. Calculate total similarity\n        $totalSimilarity = $this->calculateTotalSimilarity($matchedSources, count($chunks));\n\n        // 6. Build report\n        $report = [\n            'checked_at' => now()->toISOString(),\n            'provider' => 'internal',\n            'word_count' => $wordCount,\n            'chunk_count' => count($chunks),\n            'sources_checked' => Ethesis::where('is_public', true)->count(),\n            'matches_found' => count($matchedSources),\n            'top_matches' => array_slice($matchedSources, 0, 10),\n        ];\n\n        return [\n            'score' => round($totalSimilarity, 2),\n            'sources' => $matchedSources,\n            'report' => $report,\n        ];\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Compare document chunks with E-Thesis database\n     */\n    protected function compareWithDatabase(array $chunks, int $excludeMemberId): array\n    {\n        $matches = [];\n        \n        // Get all E-Thesis fingerprints (excluding the member's own documents)\n        $etheses = Ethesis::where('is_public', true)\n            ->whereHas('fingerprint')\n            ->with('fingerprint', 'department')\n            ->get();\n\n        foreach ($etheses as $ethesis) {\n            if (!$ethesis->fingerprint || empty($ethesis->fingerprint->content_chunks)) {\n                continue;\n            }\n\n            $similarity = $this->compareChunks($chunks, $ethesis->fingerprint->content_chunks);\n            \n            if ($similarity > 1) { // More than 1% match\n                $matches[] = [\n                    'source_type' => 'ethesis',\n                    'source_id' => $ethesis->id,\n                    'title' => $ethesis->title,\n                    'author' => $ethesis->author,\n                    'year' => $ethesis->year,\n                    'department' => $ethesis->department?->name,\n                    'similarity' => round($similarity, 2),\n                ];\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Sort by similarity descending\n        usort($matches, fn($a, $b) => $b['similarity'] <=> $a['similarity']);\n\n        return $matches;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Compare two sets of chunks using Jaccard similarity\n     */\n    protected function compareChunks(array $sourceChunks, array $targetChunks): float\n    {\n        if (empty($sourceChunks) || empty($targetChunks)) {\n            return 0;\n        }\n\n        $matchedChunks = 0;\n        $totalCheckableChunks = count($sourceChunks);\n\n        foreach ($sourceChunks as $sourceChunk) {\n            $sourceWords = explode(' ', $sourceChunk);\n            $sourceSet = array_flip($sourceWords);\n            \n            foreach ($targetChunks as $targetChunk) {\n                $targetWords = explode(' ', $targetChunk);\n                \n                // Calculate Jaccard similarity for this chunk pair\n                $intersection = count(array_intersect_key($sourceSet, array_flip($targetWords)));\n                $union = count($sourceWords) + count($targetWords) - $intersection;\n                \n                if ($union > 0) {\n                    $chunkSimilarity = ($intersection / $union) * 100;\n                    \n                    // If more than 60% similar, consider it a match\n                    if ($chunkSimilarity > 60) {\n                        $matchedChunks++;\n                        break; // Move to next source chunk\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n\n        // Return percentage of matched chunks\n        return ($matchedChunks / $totalCheckableChunks) * 100;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Calculate total similarity score from matches\n     */\n    protected function calculateTotalSimilarity(array $matches, int $totalChunks): float\n    {\n        if (empty($matches)) {\n            return 0;\n        }\n\n        // Sum all similarities (capped at 100%)\n        $total = array_sum(array_column($matches, 'similarity'));\n        \n        // Average across matches or use max, depending on preference\n        // Using weighted average where higher matches count more\n        return min($total, 100);\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Extract text from document\n     */\n    public function extractText(string $filePath, string $fileType): string\n    {\n        try {\n            if (strtolower($fileType) === 'pdf') {\n                return $this->extractTextFromPdf($filePath);\n            } elseif (in_array(strtolower($fileType), ['docx', 'doc'])) {\n                return $this->extractTextFromDocx($filePath);\n            }\n        } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n            Log::error(\"Text extraction failed: \" . $e->getMessage());\n            throw new \\Exception(\"Gagal mengekstrak teks: \" . $e->getMessage());\n        }\n\n        return '';\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Extract text from PDF file\n     */\n    protected function extractTextFromPdf(string $filePath): string\n    {\n        $parser = new PdfParser();\n        $pdf = $parser->parseFile($filePath);\n        \n        $text = '';\n        foreach ($pdf->getPages() as $page) {\n            $text .= $page->getText() . \"\\n\";\n        }\n        \n        return $text;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Extract text from DOCX file\n     */\n    protected function extractTextFromDocx(string $filePath): string\n    {\n        $zip = new \\ZipArchive();\n        \n        if ($zip->open($filePath) !== true) {\n            throw new \\Exception('Cannot open DOCX file');\n        }\n\n        $content = $zip->getFromName('word/document.xml');\n        $zip->close();\n\n        if (!$content) {\n            return '';\n        }\n\n        // Strip XML tags and get text content\n        $text = strip_tags($content);\n        \n        // Clean up whitespace\n        $text = preg_replace('/\\s+/', ' ', $text);\n        \n        return trim($text);\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * iThenticate/Turnitin API integration\n     */\n    protected function checkIthenticate(PlagiarismCheck $check): array\n    {\n        $provider = new Providers\\IthenticateProvider();\n        \n        if (!$provider->isConfigured()) {\n            Log::warning(\"iThenticate not configured, falling back to internal check\");\n            return $this->checkInternal($check);\n        }\n\n        $result = $provider->submit($check);\n        \n        // Get viewer URL if available\n        if ($check->external_id) {\n            $reportUrl = $provider->getReportUrl($check->external_id);\n            if ($reportUrl) {\n                $check->update(['external_report_url' => $reportUrl]);\n            }\n        }\n\n        return $result;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Turnitin integration (uses same API as iThenticate)\n     */\n    protected function checkTurnitin(PlagiarismCheck $check): array\n    {\n        // Turnitin and iThenticate use the same TCA API\n        return $this->checkIthenticate($check);\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Placeholder for Copyleaks integration\n     */\n    protected function checkCopyleaks(PlagiarismCheck $check): array\n    {\n        // TODO: Implement Copyleaks API integration\n        throw new \\Exception('Copyleaks integration belum tersedia. Hubungi administrator.');\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Get provider name\n     */\n    public function getProvider(): string\n    {\n        return $this->provider;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Check if plagiarism checking is enabled\n     */\n    public static function isEnabled(): bool\n    {\n        return (bool) Setting::get('plagiarism_enabled', true);\n    }\n}"

                    "Text": "        // Store external ID\n        $check->update([\n            'external_id' => $data['id'],\n        ]);\n\n        Log::info(\"iThenticate: Submission created with ID: \" . $data['id']);\n\n        return $data;\n    }\n\n    /**\n     * Upload file to submission\n     */\n    protected function uploadFile(PlagiarismCheck $check, string $submissionId): void\n    {\n        $filePath = Storage::disk('local')->path($check->file_path);\n        $fileContent = file_get_contents($filePath);\n        \n        $response = Http::withHeaders([\n            'Authorization' => 'Bearer ' . $this->apiSecret,\n            'X-Turnitin-Integration-Name' => $this->integrationName ?: 'Library-Portal-API',\n            'X-Turnitin-Integration-Version' => '1.0.0',\n            'Content-Type' => 'binary/octet-stream',\n            'Content-Disposition' => 'inline; filename=\"' . $check->original_filename . '\"',\n        ])\n        ->withBody($fileContent, 'binary/octet-stream')\n        ->put(\"{$this->baseUrl}/api/v1/submissions/{$submissionId}/original\");\n\n        if (!$response->successful()) {\n            Log::error(\"iThenticate uploadFile failed: \" . $response->body());\n            throw new \\Exception('Gagal mengupload file: ' . $response->json('message', 'Unknown error'));"
                  }
                ],
                "status": "Success"
              }
            ]

                  {
                    "Text": "<?php\n\nnamespace App\\Jobs;\n\nuse App\\Models\\PlagiarismCheck;\nuse App\\Services\\Plagiarism\\CertificateGenerator;\nuse App\\Services\\Plagiarism\\PlagiarismService;\nuse Illuminate\\Bus\\Queueable;\nuse Illuminate\\Contracts\\Queue\\ShouldQueue;\nuse Illuminate\\Foundation\\Bus\\Dispatchable;\nuse Illuminate\\Queue\\InteractsWithQueue;\nuse Illuminate\\Queue\\SerializesModels;\nuse Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Log;\n\nclass ProcessPlagiarismCheck implements ShouldQueue\n{\n    use Dispatchable, InteractsWithQueue, Queueable, SerializesModels;\n\n    public int $tries = 5; // Allow retries for transient errors\n    public int $timeout = 2100; // 35 minutes for Turnitin processing (30 min polling + buffer)\n    public int $backoff = 120; // Retry after 2 minutes if needed\n\n    public function __construct(\n        public PlagiarismCheck $check\n    ) {}\n\n    public function handle(PlagiarismService $service): void\n    {\n        Log::info(\"Processing plagiarism check #{$this->check->id}\");\n\n        // Update status to processing\n        $this->check->update([\n            'status' => PlagiarismCheck::STATUS_PROCESSING,\n            'started_at' => now(),\n            'error_message' => null,\n        ]);\n\n        try {\n            // Perform the check\n            $result = $service->check($this->check);\n\n            // Update with results\n            $this->check->update([\n                'status' => PlagiarismCheck::STATUS_COMPLETED,\n                'similarity_score' => $result['score'],\n                'similarity_sources' => $result['sources'],\n                'detailed_report' => $result['report'],\n                'provider' => $service->getProvider(),\n                'completed_at' => now(),\n            ]);\n\n            Log::info(\"Plagiarism check #{$this->check->id} completed. Score: {$result['score']}%\");\n\n            // Generate certificate\n            $generator = new CertificateGenerator($this->check);\n            $generator->generate();\n\n            Log::info(\"Certificate generated for check #{$this->check->id}\");\n\n        } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n            Log::error(\"Plagiarism check #{$this->check->id} failed: \" . $e->getMessage());\n\n            $this->check->update([\n                'status' => PlagiarismCheck::STATUS_FAILED,\n                'error_message' => $e->getMessage(),\n                'completed_at' => now(),\n            ]);\n\n            // Re-throw to trigger retry if applicable\n            if ($this->attempts() < $this->tries) {\n                throw $e;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    public function failed(\\Throwable $exception): void\n    {\n        Log::error(\"Plagiarism check job failed permanently for #{$this->check->id}: \" . $exception->getMessage());\n\n        $this->check->update([\n            'status' => PlagiarismCheck::STATUS_FAILED,\n            'error_message' => 'Proses gagal setelah beberapa percobaan: ' . $exception->getMessage(),\n            'completed_at' => now(),\n        ]);\n    }\n}"
                  }

Score: {$result['score']}%\");\n\n            // Generate certificate\n            $generator = new CertificateGenerator($this->check);\n            $generator->generate();\n\n            // Send email notification\n            $this->sendNotification();\n\n        } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n            Log::error(\"Plagiarism check #{$this->check->id} failed: \" . $e->getMessage());\n\n            $this->check->update([\n                'status' => PlagiarismCheck::STATUS_FAILED,\n                'error_message' => $e->getMessage(),\n                'completed_at' => now(),\n            ]);\n\n            if ($this->attempts() < $this->tries) {\n                throw $e;\n            }\n            \n            // Send failure notification on last attempt\n            $this->sendNotification();\n        }\n    }\n\n    public function failed(\\Throwable $exception): void\n    {\n        Log::error(\"Plagiarism check job failed permanently for #{$this->check->id}: \" . $exception->getMessage());\n\n        $this->check->update([\n            'status' => PlagiarismCheck::STATUS_FAILED,\n            'error_message' => 'Proses gagal setelah beberapa percobaan: ' . $exception->getMessage(),\n            'completed_at' => now(),\n        ]);\n\n        $this->sendNotification();\n    }\n\n    protected function sendNotification(): void\n    {\n        try {\n            $member = $this->check->member;\n            if ($member && $member->email) {\n                $member->notify(new PlagiarismCheckCompleted($this->check->fresh()));\n                Log::info(\"Email notification sent for check #{$this->check->id}\");\n            }\n        } catch (\\Exception $e) {\n            Log::error(\"Failed to send notification for check #{$this->check->id}: \" . $e->getMessage());\n        }\n    }\n}",

    "`ga_enabled` sudah diaktifkan, tapi **`ga_measurement_id` masih kosong**. \n\nAnda perlu memasukkan Measurement ID dari Google Analytics. Formatnya seperti `G-XXXXXXXXXX`. Dapatkan dari:\n1. Buka Google Analytics  Admin  Data Streams  pilih stream  copy Measurement ID\n\nSetelah dapat ID-nya, masukkan via:\n- **Filament Admin**  Settings  Analytics  isi Measurement ID\n- Atau beritahu saya ID-nya dan saya update langsung di database\n\nTanpa Measurement ID, script Google Analytics tidak akan dimuat karena kondisi di layout:\n```php\n@if($gaEnabled && $gaMeasurementId)  // <- ga_measurement_id kosong = false\n```\n[Tool uses: none]",
    "> Service Account JSON (Ini dapatnya dmna?)",
    "Service Account JSON didapat dari Google Cloud Console. Berikut langkahnya:\n\n## Cara Mendapatkan Service Account JSON\n\n1. **Buka Google Cloud Console**\n   - https://console.cloud.google.com\n\n2. **Pilih/Buat Project**\n   - Pilih project yang sama dengan Google Analytics Anda\n\n3. **Buat Service Account**\n   - Menu  **IAM & Admin**  **Service Accounts**\n   - Klik **+ CREATE SERVICE ACCOUNT**\n   - Isi nama (misal: `analytics-reader`)\n   - Klik **CREATE AND CONTINUE**\n   - Skip role (tidak perlu)\n   - Klik **DONE**\n\n4. **Generate JSON Key**\n   - Klik service account yang baru dibuat\n   - Tab **KEYS**  **ADD KEY**  **Create new key**\n   - Pilih **JSON**  **CREATE**\n   - File JSON akan terdownload otomatis\n\n5. **Hubungkan ke Google Analytics**\n   - Buka **Google Analytics**  **Admin**\n   - **Property Settings**  **Property Access Management**\n   - Klik **+**  **Add users**\n   - Masukkan email service account (format: `nama@project-id.iam.gserviceaccount.com`)\n   - Beri role **Viewer**\n   - Save\n\n6. **Dapatkan Property ID**\n   - Di Google Analytics  **Admin**  **Property Settings**\n   - Copy **Property ID** (angka, bukan Measurement ID)\n\n---\n\n**Catatan:** Service Account JSON hanya diperlukan jika Anda ingin menampilkan **statistik analytics di dashboard admin** (visitor count, page views, dll). \n\nJika hanya ingin **tracking pengunjung** di website, cukup isi:\n-  `ga_measurement_id` (G-XXXXXXXXXX)\n-  `ga_enabled` = 1\n\nService Account JSON opsional untuk fitur lanjutan.\n[Tool uses: none]",

    "> www data itu user juga kh?",
    "Ya, `www-data` adalah system user yang dibuat otomatis saat install Nginx/Apache.\n\n**Perbedaan:**\n\n| | www-data | vm-4 |\n|---|---|---|\n| Tipe | System user | Regular user |\n| Login | Tidak bisa login SSH | Bisa login SSH |\n| Home | `/var/www` | `/home/vm-4` |\n| Tujuan | Menjalankan web server | User manusia |\n| Shell | `/usr/sbin/nologin` | `/bin/bash` |\n\n**Kenapa ada www-data?**\n- Security: Jika web server di-hack, attacker hanya dapat akses terbatas (bukan root)\n- Isolasi: Proses web terpisah dari user lain\n\n**Saat ini:**\n- Nginx  jalan sebagai www-data\n- PHP-FPM  jalan sebagai www-data\n- Files  mix owner (vm-4 dan www-data)\n\n**Opsi 2 akan ubah:**\n- PHP-FPM  jalan sebagai vm-4\n- Files  semua owned vm-4\n- Nginx  tetap www-data (hanya baca file, tidak perlu write)\n[Tool uses: none]",

EPrints create/update user session\n\n**Keuntungan:**\n- Single Sign-On (SSO) - login sekali untuk semua sistem\n- User management terpusat di Laravel\n- Tidak perlu sync password\n- Member perpustakaan otomatis bisa akses repository\n\n### Implementasi di EPrints\n\nBuat file `/usr/share/eprints3/archives/repounida/cfg/cfg.d/z_oauth_login.pl`:\n\n```perl\n# OAuth Login via Laravel Library System\n$c->{check_user_password} = sub {\n    my( $repo, $username, $password ) = @_;\n    \n    # Call Laravel API to verify\n    use LWP::UserAgent;\n    use JSON;\n    \n    my $ua = LWP::UserAgent->new;\n    my $response = $ua->post(\n        'https://library.unida.gontor.ac.id/api/auth/verify',\n        Content_Type => 'application/json',\n        Content => encode_json({\n            email => $username,\n            password => $password\n        })\n    );\n    \n    if ($response->is_success) {\n        my $data = decode_json($response->content);\n        return $data->{valid} ? $username : undef;\n    }\n    \n    # Fallback to local EPrints auth\n    return undef;\n};\n```\n\n---\n\n##  Promosi Library di EPrints\n\n### 1.
